node.text:
Guess who’s back?? Back again!! 

Old Forester is releasing the newest expression of The 117 Series, Warehouse K, available exclusively at Old Forester Distilling CO. and select Kentucky retailers. 
 
The 117 Series, is the first Old Forester bourbon to feature a woman’s signature on the bottle, debuted with a high angel’s share release and is now being followed by the Warehouse K release. This limited-edition release is sold in 375ml bottles and pays homage to Old Forester’s homeplace located on Whiskey Row. For brand fans and bourbon connoisseurs, Warehouse K has gained a cult following for featuring a blend of barrels aged on different floors. 

Bottled at 110 proof, and available starting Aug 12 at the retail shop at @oldforester for $49.99 in limited quantities, and at select Kentucky stores! 

I had the first release and it was delicious! Go get it!!
.
.
.
